FROM title t, cast_info ci, movie_keyword mk
WHERE t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.kind_id  =  6 AND t.production_year  =  2006 AND ci.person_id  >  2147052 AND mk.keyword_id  >  585
